</P>
<P>
   Investment firm Sands Brothers &AMP; Co. Ltd. initiated coverage of
SDLI with a ''strong buy'' rating. SDLI makes semiconductor lasers
and fiber-optic products and is one of several companies
flourishing on heavy demand for those products.
</P>
