<DOCNO> APW20000613.0130 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-13 17:38 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Man charged in air rage incident pleads innocent  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
