the game on Jason Tyner's sacrifice fly.
</P>
<P>
   Jay Payton walked to lead off the fifth and reached third on
Derek Bell's single. Cubs starter Kevin Tapani struck out the next
two batters before Robin Ventura drove in both runners with a
double to make it 3-1.
