Stadium as scheduled, and a makeup night game at Yankee Stadium.
It's the first time since Sept. 7, 1903, that two major league
games will be played between the same teams on the same day at
different stadiums. ... Carlton Fisk, who will be inducted into the
Hall of Fame in July, sang ''Take Me Out to the Ballgame'' during
the seventh-inning stretch.
